Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.93,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Stronghold of Lust
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Where is Pleguzes Jiart?>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<You may begin.>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Your Majesty!>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see the oracle's prophecy fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have conducted multiple\Nreconnaissance missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it is now time \Nto launch a massive strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear how you \Ncame to that conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that this encompassing strike\Nis not a waste of time, Dolgana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, there is no \Npoint in making such
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a maneuver if it fails to \Nusher staggering results.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that some of the primitives\Nare capable of flying like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the ones who kicked your butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-if I had more time, I could have\Nturned them into a sea of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolgana, let us hear your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I would like\NKlein to fight in the vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will follow behind and \Nhunt down the lamata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you have me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Babysit Lumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lutiel, I would like you and Lumes\Nto finish off the remaining lamata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolgana, you will be in \Ncharge of this Ta Hevara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the gods be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does everyone find working together\Nfor the shikaara amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that this journey's prophecy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is of a scale that comes \Nonly once every 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lamata have resisted beyond our-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thrill of the hunt comes from everyone\Nrelying upon their own skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I'm going \Nto put this to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The impatient brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here, Lutiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wine is most delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you see to your preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave after one more glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I get to mount in my manor\Nafter this Ta Hevara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This prophecy is not meant\Nfor your personal gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleguzes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The parisada just adjourned \Na few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tend to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have appreciated\Nyour attendance, Pleguzes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Your Majesty-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot measure him by
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your set of standards, not my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, would you care for a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must prepare for Ta Hevara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purify yourself and prepare for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell my brother on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleguzes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Jiart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like how it is more humble than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's woman was also humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was not to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made her boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I may not amply satisfy you,\NPrince Pleguzes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the very image of a Manaava.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You obey your instincts\Nas you obtain anything you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those lamata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly they consider \Nit a disgrace to obey
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one's instinct and drown in desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there dignity in \Nthe instinct of the living?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill those you wish to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And rape those you wish to rape,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yes, Pleguzes Jiart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that race of lamata\Ncan defy our instincts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Why exactly are we implementing\Nthis kind of operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I already explained,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were successfully able to \Nshrink the light wave weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it takes time to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it is unable \Nto fire a chain of shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we must rely on tactics that-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sir, I wasn't done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can figure out the rest from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, more importantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could anything use some sprucing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander in Chief Zorig of the GDF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will explain the situation \Nleading to the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our GDF army was originally formed\Nas a space security force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The economic powers of the world\Nestablished their own armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those armies were unified as one,\Nbecoming the GDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:09:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, the Wulgaru hit us\Nwith a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it was our first encounter\Nwith foes from outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was difficult for us to respond\Nin a unified manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've finally reached
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the point where we are capable \Nof full-scale operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon multiple analyses primarily
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nconducted by the Operations Command,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have completed what we believe to be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe best strategy for this upcoming battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We consider it imperative that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the media and the people of \Nthe world offer their support.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we would like to disclose\Nthe content of our strategy in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would, Vice \NChief of Staff Komine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lt. Amane, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it almost time for you to explain\Nthe strategy to the media?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you were the central figure\Nbehind devising this plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain our strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The GDF's recent assault on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy base on Planetoid \NRA221 ended in success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we believe that the enemy\Nis preparing to retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we have decided \Nto destroy Ragazza,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy's frontline base,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is located in close proximity\Nto our army base on Ceres.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First we will attack
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy with our\Ncutting-edge laser-based system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent the enemy from rushing us,\Nwe will set up a minefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the mobile troops will
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nfire in unison with disposable rail guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, we will enter normal battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having predicted the enemy's path,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwe have positioned vessels in front of Ceres
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will fire a volley of guided
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sublight speed guns and \Nfree electron cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, we will focus \Non absolute defense
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nuntil the light wave weapon is fully charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the heavy tactical \Nlaser has charged,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the vanguard mobile troops \Nand vessels will leave
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the laser's line of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon evacuation, we will destroy the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wulgaru base along with their fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the Battle of Ceres,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the GDF will do everything within \Nits power to win this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will be in charge of \Nmanaging your schedules,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Peko Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-the pleasure's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is boarding the mother ship with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be supervising your schedules\Nand everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into any difficulties\Nin your work or daily lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please feel free to \Ncome see me for advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even give you tips on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I could \Nuse some personal advi-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we supposed to participate \Nin that Battle of Ceres
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they just announced?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but you'll be on \Nstandby for a while first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to do as \Nyou like on Star Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have a meeting to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared new rooms\Nfor everyone on Star Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also use it for purchases\Nin the mess hall and at kiosks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me know if \Nyou need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets their own room, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a VIP room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so different from the dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, go to your own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to our rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are all of you doing in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, it felt right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My room gives me the willies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These rooms are too big \Nfor just one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-why don't we check out the mess hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Do you have \Npickled fish guts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not terribly hungry, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izurucchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doncha join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like something?\NI'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd recommend the \Nyakiniku meal for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-then I'll have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your schooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem too happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I don't have \Na home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you going to come back\Nhere from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of us as your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're something like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to return,\Nonce you've taken off in flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to return,\Nonce you've taken off in flight,\NMigratory Bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to respond to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you see, I don't have any\Nmemories of my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not sure what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But supposedly I had foster \Nparents for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time \Nsince I left the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this vessel feels like home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think of Degawa as my father and\NDan as my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, heroes are supposed to be loners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel like I ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle of Ceres is \Ndisconcerting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my pit crew also wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI couldn't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing better\Nwith yours than I am mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally! You've got it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna swap with Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Kei's crew filled with hot babes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, mine's filled with...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My crew seems like it \Nwas originally a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is where we're \Npermanently stationed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndo you think they'll want to talk every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be rough having a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just made me feel a bit better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not having a family might actually\Nmake life pretty carefree, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why is everyone in my room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to copy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't the place for \Nmanga-drawing brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you sneak in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of our pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is doing a splendid \Njob fighting the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one out there protecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru, you can really draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me the hero in your next piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes with families \Ncan be nice too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Godinion.\NRequesting permission for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is control.\NGodinion is cleared for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleared for takeoff. All ranges: Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Increasing backup engine output.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before start check: Complete.\NIncreasing backup engine output.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before start check: Complete.\NExternal power has been established.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disconnect all equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start all engines!\NDisconnect all equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Internal pressure increasing. \NTurbines activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Main engine military!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've checked their heavy armament,\Nexchanged malfunctioning parts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and swapped anything that has\Ngiven any errors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just need one last fine tuning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle of Ceres is our \Nfirst big battle, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true for the AHSMB, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the AHSMB units\Ndon't decide to turn tail and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The JURIA-SYSTEM...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's insane how much it improves\Nthe machine's response time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's extremely difficult to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an amazing yet annoying system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it responds too strongly\Nto the pilot, it falls apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine we'll use their full armament\Nand pit crews for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of the F1's crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been working on how to repair
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the AHSMB while they're \Nin the midst of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the pit crews\Nwill offer their full support!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleguzes Jiart, thank you \Nfor your participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that we will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of\Nparticipating in the shikaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here only here in \Ncase Teoria shows herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleguzesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That which I want never \Nfalls within my grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It drives my lusts and \Nstimulates my instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this pretty close to Ceres?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are we gonna sortie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When'll that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, where's Suruga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of the usual fare,\NI've got massive anti-ship guided missiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,high-mobility guided missiles\Nand a midrange impact cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be strappin' tough guns,\Nbut you're still squishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do push-ups together \Nuntil it's time to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweating with guys \Njust isn't my thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-that aside, can I \Nglue this on somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All AHSMB pilots, board your units!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to sortie! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've boarded,\Nwait there until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best to remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:21:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shrink from battle,\Nthe AHSMBs will focus on defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Asagicchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why the heck did you call me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru was trying to help \Nyou loosen up, Asagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The goal behind DNA is to survive\Nand create copies of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The JURIA-SYSTEM awakens \Nvarious instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consequentially, it horribly\Nshakes the pilot's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation commences in T-30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy vessels at Point Tango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is attacking our\Nprimary line of defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They out-maneuvered us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire your railgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!\NFire your railgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:22:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost 70% of the \N1st Mobile Strike Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! We aren't ready to-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! Commence the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:55.91,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle of Ceres
